          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1630422064667-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[510ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-8 min or until the sauce has thickened and the tomato has broken down</p><p>Once thickened, return the <strong>golden paneer</strong> to the pan</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1630422068330-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1630422068330-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
