          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1630422068330-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cashew nuts </strong>to a <strong>pestle & mortar </strong>and bash into a fine powder (or blitz in a <strong>food processor</strong>)</p><p>Add 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and mix to form a paste</p><p>Stir the <strong>cashew paste </strong>into the pan and cook for 2 min further – this is your <strong>South Indian-style paneer cashew curry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1630422072942-x200.jpg",
