            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>South Indian-style paneer cashew curry</strong> with the <strong>cardamom rice</strong>, discard the <strong>cardamom pods</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions</strong> and <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> and <strong>reserved chopped</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
